#### Error Handling:
- The code includes several checks for potential errors, such as:
  ```c
  if (IS_ERR_OR_NULL(pstate)) {
      rc = PTR_ERR(pstate);
      DPU_ERROR("%s: failed to get plane%d state, %d\n", dpu_crtc->name, plane->base.id, rc);
